ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectFinancial year of The amalgamed Federal Bridge Corporation Limited
PrecisOrder (a) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2000-17 of January 12, 2000; (b) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2002-930 of May 31, 2002; and (c) setting the financial year of The Federal Bridge Corporation Limited to begin on April 1 in one year and end on March 31 in the following year.
